# API Keys for Plates Mobile App

# Google Gemini API Key
# Used for text generation and Gemini Live API (online speech-to-text)
# Get your API key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# OpenAI API Key (for Whisper speech-to-text fallback)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# OpenWeather API Key (already in use)
# Get your API key from: https://home.openweathermap.org/api_keys
OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweather_api_key_here

# Speech-to-Text Configuration
# The app uses a dual-mode speech-to-text system:
# - Online mode: Uses Google's Gemini Live API for real-time transcription
# - Offline mode: Uses Hugging Face's Candle with Whisper model locally
# The system automatically switches between modes based on network connectivity